alogy%20buff%20myself%20who%20has%20occasionally%20tried%20doing%20celebrity%20family%20trees%20for%20fun%2C%20I%20was%20curious.%20(The%20slave%20owner%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20great-great-great%20grandfather%20on%20his%20mother's%20side).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20work%20already%20done%2C%20I%20was%20already%20halfway%20there%20with%20being%20able%20to%20verify%20a%20cousin%20relationship%20with%20the%20reality%20star.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Ben%20and%20Casey%20Affleck%20are%20famously%20from%20Boston%2C%20their%20Affleck%20side%20of%20the%20family%20is%20not%20from%20Massachusetts.%20Their%20father%20and%20grandfather%2C%20Myron%20Affleck%2C%20Jr.%2C%20were%20born%20in%20Rhode%20Island.%20The%20next%20two%20generations%20back%20of%20Afflecks%20were%20from%20Yonkers%2C%20New%20York.%20Finally%2C%20we%20get%20to%20William%20Affleck%2C%20born%20in%201824%20in%20Glasgow%2C%20Scotland%2C%20who%20immigrated%20to%20Yonkers%20in%201848%20and%20worked%20in%20the%20railroad%20industry%2C%20according%20to%20his%201906%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesmachine.nytimes.com%2Ftimesmachine%2F1906%2F03%2F13%2F101769594.html%3FpageNumber%3D9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eobituary%20in%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20on%20Zac%20Affleck's%20side%2C%20his%20male%20Affleck%20ancestors%20have%20been%20in%20Utah%20for%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20search%2C%20I%20found%20no%20overlap%20or%20common%20ancestry%20between%20the%20two%20Affleck%20families%20in%20the%20United%20States%20going%20back%20to%20the%201800s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(For%20transparency%2C%20information%20about%20Zac's%20living%20father%20and%20grandfather%20came%20from%20newspaper%20notices%20and%20other%20public%20records.%20For%20older%20generations%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20U.S.%20Census%20records%2C%20birth%20and%20death%20records%2C%20and%20other%20records%20available%20on%20Ancestry.com).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225dd73755-8f19-4e73-9a