having%20the%20oldest%20continually%20running%20congregation%20of%20the%20LDS%20church.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthechurchnews.com%2Fliving-faith%2F2024%2F07%2F23%2Fpreston-ward-branch-longest-continually-running-unit-church%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPreston%20branch%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20established%20by%20missionaries%20in%201837%20%E2%80%94%20a%20decade%20before%20the%20Mormons%20settled%20in%20Utah%20in%201847.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Preston%20Affleck%20was%20born%20in%201801%20in%20Scotland%20and%20moved%20to%20England%20sometime%20before%201825%2C%20eventually%20settling%20in%20Preston.%20According%20to%20a%20written%20family%20history%20by%20a%20relative%2C%20William%20converted%20to%20the%20new%20religion%20after%20meeting%20missionaries%20there.%20Although%20he%20died%20before%20being%20able%20to%20leave%20England%2C%20he%20urged%20his%20children%20and%20wife%20to%20go%20to%20%26quot%3BZion%26quot%3B%20(Utah)%2C%20where%20they%20settled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20branches%20of%20Zac's%20family%20also%20have%20deep%20roots%20in%20the%20church.%20His%20fifth%20great-grandfather%2C%20William%20Smith%20Muir%2C%20was%20born%20in%20Scotland%20in%201822.%20Muir%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Mormons%20who%20followed%20Joseph%20Smith%20to%20Nauvoo%2C%20Illinois%2C%20and%20later%20went%20to%20Utah.%20Muir%20was%20a%20notable%20pioneer%2C%20enough%20so%20that%20there%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Flifeofwilliamsmi00muir%2Fmode%2F2up%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E166-page%20family%20history%20written%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20him%20as%20well%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fsouthwickresearch.com%2FGenealogy%2FWilliam%2520S%2520Muir%2520Coloring%2520Book-11.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren's%20coloring%20book%20about%20him%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20impossible%20to%20say%20definitively%20that%20Zac%20Affleck%20and%20Ben%20Affleck%20are%20not%20very%20distant%20cousins.%20It's%20possible%20they%20shared%20a%20common%20relative%20in%20Scotland%20from%20before%201800.%20As%20Scottish%20surnames%20go%2C%20Affleck%20isn't%20the%20most%20common%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20not%20incredibly%20rare%20(I%20have%20a%20great-great-grandparent%20with%20the%20last%20name%20Affleck%2C%20for%20example)%20and%20there%20are%20Afflecks%20all%20over%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20sharing%20a%20last%20name%20is%20a%20pretty%20good%20clue%20that%20there%20may%20be%20a%20family%20connection%20somewhere%20in%20history%2C%20it's%20not%20certain.%20The%20origins%20of%20the%20Affleck%20surname%20date%20back%20to%20the%201200s%2C%20so%20there%20are%20centuries%20of%20potential%20for%20a%20common%20ancestor%20of%20the%20two%20separate%20William%20Afflecks%20of%20the%201800s%20whose%20descendants%2C%20200%20years%20later%2C%20would%20end%20up%20on%20reality%20TV%20and%20in%20movies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20the%20public%20records%20show%2C%20however%2C%20is%20that%20Zac%20Affleck%20and%20Ben%20Affleck%20are%20not%20second%20cousins%2C%20or%20third%20cousins%2C%20or%20even%20fourth%20cousins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reached%20out%20to%20reps%20for%20Zac%2C%20Jen%2C%20and%20Ben%20Affleck%2C%20but%20did%20not%20receive%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjen-zac-affleck-related-to-ben-affleck-explained-mormon-wives-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726783479000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e2d6a9d17aa3c7b2b1d5df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjen-zac-affleck-related-to-ben-affleck-explained-mormon-wives-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThe%20Secret%20Lives%20of%20Mormon%20Wives%26quot%3B%20star%20Jen%20Affleck%20has%20claimed%20her%20husband%20Zac%20is%20a%20first%20or%20second%20cousin%20of%20Ben%20Affleck's.%20According%20to%2