out%20China's%20Growing%20Presence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20south%20Asian%20and%20Indian%20Ocean%20region%20is%20going%20through%20a%20%26quot%3Bdifficult%20time%26quot%3B%2C%20Sri%20Lankan%20President%20Ranil%20Wickremesinghe%20said%20on%20Thursday%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV.%20Sri%20Lanka%20will%20hold%20elections%20on%20September%2021%20to%20elect%20the%20next%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Wickremesinghe%2C%20who%20took%20over%20as%20President%20when%20Sri%20Lanka%20was%20going%20through%20its%20worst-ever%20economic%20crisis%2C%20has%20steered%20the%20economy%20back%20towards%20normalcy.%20His%20re-election%20will%20prove%20to%20be%20an%20effective%20referendum%20on%20an%20unpopular%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20austerity%20plan%20enacted%20by%20his%20government%20after%20the%20island%20nation's%20unprecedented%20financial%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanil%20Wickremesinghe%2C%2075%2C%20is%20seeking%20a%20fresh%20mandate%20after%20claiming%20credit%20for%20stabilising%20the%20economy%20and%20bringing%20an%20end%20to%20months%20of%20food%2C%20fuel%20and%20medicine%20shortages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV's%20Gaurie%20Dwivedi%2C%20Mr%20Wickremesinghe%20spoke%20not%20just%20about%20the%20domestic%20challenges%20Sri%20Lanka%20faces%2C%20but%20also%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20the%20entire%20south%20Asian%20region%2C%20where%20India%20plays%20a%20leading%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECRISES%20IN%20MALDIVES%20AND%20BANGLADESH%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20difficult%20time%20for%20the%20region.%20Maldives%20is%20going%20through%20an%20economic%20crisis%20and%20needs%20all%20the%20help%20they%20can%20get.%20Bangladesh%20too%20is%20facing%20a%20political%20crisis%20and%20we%20(as%20neighbours)%20should%20ensure%20that%20stability%20returns%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%20after%20which%20elections%20can%20be%20held%20where%20a%20new%20parliament%20can%20then%20decide%20on%20a%20new%20prime%20minister%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20President%20said%2C%20while%20speaking%20about%20the%20most%20recent%20and%20immediate%20regional%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20of%20all%20the%20others%20neighbours%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20issue%20of%20Bangladesh%20has%20the%20greatest%20impact%20on%20India%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20that%20Sri%20Lanka%20too%20has%20significant%20investments%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20which%20it%20views%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfriendly%20country%26quot%3B.%20He%20said%20he%20is%20concerned%20that%20if%20the%20crisis%20in%20Bangladesh%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20resolved%20in%20the%20short-to-medium%20term%2C%20it%20can%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESRI%20LANKA'S%20CHALLENGES%20AND%20ANTI-INDIA%20REMARKS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20when%20Ranil%20Wickremesinghe%20took%20charge%20as%20President%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20was%20dealing%20with%20civil%20unrest%20spurred%20by%20the%20economic%20crisis.%20There%20were%20protests%20across%20the%20nation%20which%20led%20to%20thousands%20storming%20the%20Presidential%20palace%20which%20was%20then%20occupied%20by%20Mr%20Wickremesinghe's%20predecessor%20Gotabaya%20Rajapaksa%2C%20who%20fled%20the%20country.%20Mr%20Wickremesinghe%20took%20charge%20and%20restored%20calm%20and%20helped%20revived%20the%20economy%20by%20taking%20some%20tough%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThink%20of%20the%20time%20when%20all%20hope%20was%20lost...%20we%20didn't%20have%20food%2C%20gas%2C%20medicine%2C%20or%20any%20hopes.%20Now%20you%20have%20a%20choice.%20Decide%20if%20you%20want%20to%20go%20back%20to%20that%20period%20of%20terror%2C%20or%20progress%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Wickremesinghe%20had%20said%20in%20the%20closing%20days%20of%20his%20election%20campaign.%20India%20had%20stood%20by%20Sri%20Lanka%20during%20the%20crisis%20and%20helped%20revive%20its%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Wickremesinghe%20told%20NDTV%20that%20it%20will%20be%20his%20priority%20to%20deepen%20economic%20ties%2C%20especially%20in%20infrastructure%20projects%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20two%20nations%20have%20shared%20cultural%20and%20economic%20ties%20for%20%26quot%3Bthousands%20of%20years%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20rivals%20in%20the%20elections%20however%20have%20made%20some%20strong%20anti-India%20remarks%2C%20and%20should%20they%20win%20the%20election%2C%20it%20may%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20challenge%20for%20New%20Delhi%20and%20perhaps%20even%20a%20complete%20reset%20in%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20us%20first%20watch%20the%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20President%2C%20hinting%20at%20his%20rivals'%20remarks%20being%20amplified%20due%20to%20political%20rhetoric.%20But%20he%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20some%20groups%20which%20will%20make%20anti-India%20remarks.%20That%20can't%20be%20stopped%2C%20but%20the%20aim%20is%20to%20minimise%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20India-Sri%20Lanka%20friendship%20is%20concerned%2C%20it%20is%20decided%20by%20the%20people%20of%20both%20nations%20and%20they%20have%20already%20decided%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanil%20Wickremesinghe%20faces%20two%20formidable%20challengers%20including%20Anura%20Kumara%20Dissanayaka%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20a%20once-marginal%20Marxist%20party%20tarnished%20by%20its%20violent%20past.%20The%20party%20led%20two%20failed%20uprisings%20in%20the%201970s%20and%201980s%20that%20left%20more%20than%2080%2C000%20people%20dead%2C%20and%20won%20less%20than%20four%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20vote%20in%20the%20last%20parliamentary%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Sri%20Lanka's%20crisis%20has%20proven%20an%20opportunity%20for%20Mr%20Dissanayaka%2C%20who%20has%20seen%20a%20surge%20of%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20news%20agency%20AFP%2C%20fellow%20opposition%20leader%20Sajith%20Premadasa%2C%20once%20dismissed%20as%20the%20princeling%20dynast%20of%20a%20former%20president%20assassinated%20in%201993%20during%20the%20country's%20decades-long%20civil%20war%2C%20is%20also%20favoured%20to%20make%20a%20strong%20showing.%20He%20has%20campaigned%20on%20a%20pledge%20to%20secure%20concessions%20from%20the%20IMF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%20about%20China%2C%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20President%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BWe've%20had%20good%20relations%20with%20China%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so.%20But%20we%20will%20look%20at%20our%20interest%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20ensure%20that%20nothing%20(about%20China%20ties)%20will%20affect%20the%20security%20of%20India.%20Our%20dealings%20with%20China%20will%20work%20within%20the%20framework%26quot%3B%20of%20India's%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGROWING%20CHINESE%20PRESENCE%20IN%20INDIAN%20OCEAN%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20China%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bleading%20global%20power%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Wickremesinghe%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BChina%20is%20going%20to%20have%20an%20extended%20influence%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20region.%20They%20are%20already%20working%20with%20a%20number%20of%20countries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20looking%20to%20grow%20its%20presence%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20and%20it%20is%20already%20working%20to%20build%20up%20its%20presence%20around%20the%20Suez%20Canal%2C%20said%20Mr%20Wickremesinghe%2C%20adding%20that%20China%20is%20looking%20to%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bleading%20global%20power%20after%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSri%20Lanka%20will%20keep%20working%20with%20China%2C%20but%20we%20will%20work%20on%20our%20own%20terms%2C%20keeping%20India's%20interests%20in%20mind%2C%20after%20all%20India%20is%20just%20twenty%20miles%20away%20from%20us%20and%20we%20have%20shared%20historic%20ties%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20%26quot%3Ball-weather%20ally%26quot%3B%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bpro-Beijing%20regime%26quot%3B%20in%20Maldives%2C%20an%20increasing%20presence%20in%20Nepal%20and%20deepening%20ties%20with%20Bangladesh's%20new%20regime%2C%20China%20has%20been%20mounting%20its%20presence%20across%20south%20Asia%20and%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%20Sri%20Lanka%20votes%20on%20Saturday%20to%20elect%20their%20next%20President%2C%20one%20of%20the%20candidates%20reportedly%20being%20openly%20%26quot%3Bpro-China%20and%20anti-India%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726779900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-09%2Frcgunci_sri-lanka-ranil-reuters-_625x300_16_September_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fahead-of-sri-lankan-elections-president-ranil-wickremesinghe-tells-ndtv-about-chinas-growing-presence-6604052%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20south%20Asian%20and%20Indian%20Ocean%20region%20is%20going%20through%20a%20%26quot%3Bdifficult%20time%26quot%3B%2C%20Sri%20Lankan%20President%20Ranil%20Wickremesinghe%20said%20on%20Thursday%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV.%20Sri%20Lanka%20will%20hold%20elections%20on%20September%2021%20to%20elect%20the%20next%20President.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sri%20Lanka%20Elections%3A%20A%20Look%20At%20The%205%20Key%20Candidates%20And%20What%20They%20Stand%20For%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESri%20Lanka%2C%20which%20is%20slowly%20recovering%20from%20its%20worst-ever%20economic%20crisis%2C%20will%20vote%20to%20elect%20the%20next%20President%20on%20Saturday.%20The%20cash-strapped%20island%20nation%20is%20currently%20being%20led%20by%20President%20Ranil%20Wickremesinghe%2C%20who%20is%20seeking%20a%20re-election%20to%20continue%20with%20bold%20reforms%20to%20help%20revive%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Ranil%20Wickremesinghe%2C%2075%2C%20is%20seeking%20a%20fresh%20mandate%20after%20claiming%20credit%20for%20stabilising%20the%20economy%20and%20bringing%20an%20end%20to%20months%20of%20food%2C%20fuel%20and%20medicine%20shortages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20when%20Ranil%20Wickremesinghe%20took%20charge%20as%20President%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20was%20dealing%20with%20civil%20unrest%20spurred%20by%20the%20economic%20crisis.%20There%20were%20protests%20across%20the%20nation%20which%20led%20to%20thousands%20storming%20the%20Presidential%20palace%20which%20was%20then%20occupied%20by%20Mr%20Wickremesinghe's%20predecessor%20Gotabaya%20Rajapaksa%2C%20who%20fled%20the%20country.%20Mr%20Wickremesinghe%20took%20charge%20and%20restored%20calm%20and%20helped%20revived%20the%20economy%20by%20taking%20some%20tough%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202024%20election%20is%20key%20to%20deciding%20the%20future%20of%20reforms%20in%20the%20economically%20fragile%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20NDTV%2C%20Sri%20Lankan%20President%20Ranil%20Wickremesinghe%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20his%20vision%20for%20future%20ties%20with%20India%20holds%20a%20stronger%20economic%20relationship.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20encourage%20more%20investments%20from%20India%20and%20more%20tourists%20from%20India.%20We%20are%20working%20together%20with%20India%20on%20infrastructure%20projects%20like%20the%20Trincomalee%20Harbour%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20took%20over%20as%20President%20when%20the%20country%20was%20in%20utter%20chaos%20and%20no%20one%20thought%20we%20could%20stabilise%20this%20fast.%20But%20I%20knew%20from%20experience%20that%20we%20could%20go%20ahead%20provided%20we%20had%20the%20support%20of%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20and%20our%20creditors%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20President%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20ensured%20we%20come%20back%20to%20normalcy.%20Law%20and%20order%20is%20functioning%2C%20democracy%20is%20functioning%20and%20although%20we%20have%20stabilised%20the%20economy%2C%20now%20we%20have%20to%20decide%20our%20path.%20Are%20we%20going%20to%20get%20into%20the%20same%20old%20ways%20or%20are%20we%20working%20towards%20(building)%20a%20strong%20export%20economy%3F%20I%20have%20asked%20for%20a%20mandate%20to%20go%20ahead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Mr%20Wickremesinghe%20faces%20a%20tough%20electoral%20battle%20from%20two%20contenders.%20In%20total%2C%20President%20Wickremesinghe%20is%20among%2038%20candidates%20contesting%20Sri%20Lanka's%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20election%20is%20dominated%20by%20two%20major%20alliances%2C%20the%20SJB%20(Samagi%20Jana%20Balawegaya)%20and%20the%20NPP%20(National%20People's%20Power)%2C%20apart%20from%20various%20smaller%20parties%20and%20independent%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20the%205%20main%20contenders%20in%20the%202024%20Sri%20Lanka%20Elections%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERANIL%20WICKREMESINGHE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2F092fhub8_ranil-wickremesinghe-afp-650_625x300_13_July_22.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E75-year-old%20Ranil%20Wickremesinghe%20is%20a%20lawyer%20who%20has%20served%20as%20prime%20minister%20for%20a%20record%20six%20times.%20His%20party%20holds%20only%20one%20seat%20in%20parliament%20and%20will%20need%20to%20drum%20up%20support%20from%20key%20parties%20to%20bolster%20his%20chances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20United%20National%20Party%20or%20UNP%2C%20he%20took%20office%20in%20July%202022%20after%20widespread%20protests%20unleashed%20by%20the%20debilitating%20financial%20crisis%20forced%20his