%2C%20MEA%20Spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%20on%20Thursday%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20the%20Reuters%20report.%20It%20is%20speculative%20and%20misleading.%20It%20implies%20violations%20by%20India%2C%20where%20none%20exist%20and%2C%20hence%2C%20is%20inaccurate%20and%20mischievous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20that%20India%20has%20an%20impeccable%20track%20record%20of%20compliance%20with%20international%20obligations%20on%20the%20export%20of%20military%20and%20dual-use%20items%2C%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20been%20carrying%20out%20its%20defence%20exports%20taking%20into%20account%20its%20international%20obligations%20on%20non-proliferation%20and%20based%20on%20its%20own%20robust%20legal%20and%20regulatory%20framework%2C%20which%20includes%20a%20holistic%20assessment%20of%20relevant%20criteria%2C%20including%20end-user%20obligations%20and%20certifications.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20report%2C%20Reuters%20cited%20conversations%20with%20eleven%20Indian%20and%20European%20government%20and%20defence%20industry%20officials%20and%20an%20analysis%20of%20commercially%20available%20customs%20data%20to%20claim%20that%20artillery%20shells%20sold%20by%20Indian%20arms%20manufacturers%20had%20been%20diverted%20to%20Ukraine%20by%20European%20customers%20and%20the%20Indian%20government%20did%20not%20intervene%20to%20stop%20the%20trade%20despite%20protests%20from%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20the%20supply%20of%20munitions%2C%20which%20have%20helped%20Ukraine%20in%20the%20war%20against%20Russia%2C%20had%20been%20happening%20for%20over%20a%20year%20and%20the%20Kremlin%20had%20raised%20the%20issue%20with%20India%20at%20least%20twice%2C%20including%20in%20July%2C%20during%20a%20meeting%20between%20Foreign%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20and%20his%20Russian%20counterpart%20Sergei%20Lavrov.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20Indian%20arms%20export%20regulations%20specify%20that%20weaponry%20can%20be%20used%20onl