ection%26quot%3B%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20frequent%20elections%2C%20he%20said%2C%20are%20not%20just%20a%20financial%20liability%2C%20they%20also%20are%20a%20drain%20on%20manpower%20needed%20for%20the%20country's%20security%20system%2C%20he%20said.%20People%20from%20the%20army%20or%20paramilitary%20forces%20are%20constantly%20deployed%20to%20states%20where%20elections%20are%20due%2C%20all%20the%20year%20round.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20an%20example%2C%20he%20said%20this%20year%2C%20the%20country%20has%20witnessed%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20a%20string%20of%20state%20elections%20in%20May-June.%20%26quot%3BNow%20we%20are%20having%20the%20elections%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Haryana%20and%20after%20that%20it%20would%20be%20the%20turn%20of%20Maharashtra%2C'%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20is%20the%20question%20of%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%2C%20declared%20before%20elections%2C%20which%20puts%20brakes%20on%20development%20work.%20That%20is%20why%20elections%20should%20be%20held%20at%20one%20go%20so%20that%20%26quot%3Bonce%20it%20is%20over%2C%20governments%20can%20focus%20on%20development%20and%20its%20other%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20minister%2C%20who%20has%20been%20present%20at%20the%20cabinet%20meeting%20where%20the%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20panel's%20proposal%20was%20adopted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20multiple%20election%20also%20has%20its%20effect%20while%20drawing%20up%20the%20budget%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20somewhere%20at%20the%20back%20of%20your%20mind%20you%20know%20these%20many%20states%20will%20election%20this%20year%20and%20money%20has%20to%20be%20allotted%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20looking%20at%20the%20country's%20history%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20all%20elections%20were%20conducted%20together%20since%20the%20country%20got%20Independence%20in%201947.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20system%20continued%20till%201967.%20If%20there%20was%20no%20ill%20effect%20on%20Federalism%20then%2C%20who%20should%20it%20happen%20now%3F%20Nehru-ji%20(Jawaharlal%20Nehru)%20was%20there%20then.%20Their%20party.%20On%20today's%20date%2C%20the%20country%20needs%20%26quot%3BOne%20nation%20one%20election%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20contended%20that%20the%20%26quot%3BOne%20nation%20one%20election%26quot%3B%20plan%20is%20not%20only%20anti-democratic%20and%20unconstitutional%2C%20it%20is%20also%20impractical.%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20has%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Ban%20attempt%20to%20divert%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20public%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726760100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F0mhguo5o_chirag-paswan-yuva-conclave_625x300_19_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-problem-till-1967-chirag-paswan-to-ndtv-on-one-nation-one-election-6603570%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Simultaneous%20election%20took%20place%20in%20India%20till%201967%20and%20there%20was%20no%20problem%20at%20the%20time%20in%20terms%20of%20federalism%20or%20any%20other%20factor%2C%20Union%20minister%20Chirag%20Paswan%20said%20today%2C%20questioning%20the%20Opposition's%20resistance%20on%20the%20subject.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-problem-till-1967-chirag-paswan-to-ndtv-on-one-nation-one-election-6603570%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Genetic%20ghosts%20suggest%20Covid%E2%80%99s%20market%20origins%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726759967000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fa903%2Flive%2F98e20720-7691-11ef-a68c-41f8641ed281.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcy8095xjg4po%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20team%20of%20scientists%20say%20i