e%20report%20claims%20that%20BAC%20Consulting%20was%20under%20a%20contract%20to%20produce%20the%20devices%20on%20behalf%20of%20Gold%20Apollo%2C%20the%20Taiwanese%20company%20whose%20pagers%20exploded%20and%20killed%20nine%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20report%20added%20that%20at%20least%20two%20other%20shell%20companies%20were%20created%20as%20well%20to%20mask%20the%20real%20identities%20of%20the%20people%20creating%20the%20pagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBAC%20did%20not%20take%20ordinary%20clients%20and%20Hezbollah%20mattered%20to%20them.%20The%20batteries%20were%20laced%20with%20explosive%20Pentaerythritol%20Tetranitrate%20(PETN)%2C%20a%20very%20powerful%20explosive%20material.%20Reuters%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F3-grams-of-explosives-per-pager-israel-complex-op-to-hurt-hezbollah-6590229%5C%22%3Ethree%20grams%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20explosives%20were%20hidden%20in%20the%20new%20pagers%20and%20had%20gone%20%26quot%3Bundetected%26quot%3B%20by%20Hezbollah%20for%20months.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Hezbollah%20members%20received%20a%20message%20on%20their%20page%2C%20thinking%20it%20was%20from%20their%20commander%20but%20it%20triggered%20explosions%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fgobv8mb8_walkie-talkie-split_625x300_18_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20exploded%20walkie-talkie%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3E%26quot%3BBury%20It%20Or%20Put%20It%20In%20A%20Box%26quot%3B%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israelis%20began%20targeting%20Hezbollah%20operatives%20through%20cyberattacks%20by%20hacking%20devices%2C%20remotely%20controlling%20cameras%20of%20phones%20and%20monitoring%20the%20activities%20of%20the%20enemy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Hezbollah%20Chief%2C%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%