harply%2C%20declaring%2C%20%26quot%3BThose%20who%20wear%20blankets%20and%20drink%20ghee%20should%20measure%20their%20words.%20These%20imported%20people%2C%20whose%20own%20time%20has%20passed%2C%20are%20giving%20certificates%20to%20workers.%20We%20don't%20need%20their%20certificates.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rewa%20a%20spat%20between%20MP%20Janardan%20Mishra%20and%20MLA%20Siddharth%20Tiwari%20raised%20eyebrows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dispute%20arose%20after%20Mr%20Mishra%20made%20sharp%20remarks%20about%20late%20Congress%20leader%20Srinivas%20Tiwari%2C%20who%20is%20Mr%20Tiwari's%20grandfather.%20The%20MLA%20objected%20and%20public%20protests%20ensued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwari%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOne%20should%20not%20speak%20ill%20of%20a%20deceased%20person%20who%20dedicated%20his%20life%20to%20serving%20the%20poor.%20The%20BJP%20is%20a%20party%20driven%20by%20values...%20and%20this%20issue%20will%20be%20raised%20within%20the%20party.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMishra%2C%20however%2C%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20always%20said%20Srinivas%20Tiwari%20did%20politics%20of%20terror%2C%20loot%2C%20and%20hooliganism.%20His%20grandson%20may%20have%20joined%20BJP...%20but%20BJP%20hasn't%20joined%20him.%20If%20you're%20part%20of%20the%20family%2C%20you%20must%20also%20listen%20to%20what%20your%20baba%20did.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20in%20Raisen%20on%20Teachers'%20Day%20(September%205)%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Darsha%20Singh%20Chaudhary%20and%20Public%20Health%20Minister%20Narendra%20Shivaji%20Patel%20argued%20over%20a%20perceived%20protocol%20violation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20stemmed%20from%20an%20invitation%20card%20for%20a%20school%20event%20in%20which%20the%20MP's%20name%20was%20placed%20in%20front.%20The%20District%20Education%20Officer%20later%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20school%2C%20warning%20of%20possible%20de-recognition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leaders%20have%20downplayed%20these%20incidents%20as%20minor%20but%20the%20Congress%20is%20using%20them%20to%20criticise%20the%20party%2C%20arguing%20these%20are%20signs%20of%20deeper%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBJP%20is%20the%20largest%20party%20in%20the%20world...%20with%20leaders%20from%20the%20panchayat%20level%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20But%20we%20are%20also%20a%20party%20of%20humans.%20With%20such%20a%20large%20number%20of%20people%2C%20small%20issues%20are%20bound%20to%20arise.%20We%20have%20a%20system%20to%20address%20these%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20state%20unit%20boss%20VD%20Sharma%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI've%20spoken%20to%20everyone%20involved%20and%20this%20is%20normal%20in%20any%20large%20organisation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Congress'%20media-in-charge%20for%20the%20state%2C%20Mukesh%20Nayak%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BInfighting%20in%20the%20BJP%20is%20increasing...%20but%20this%20is%20not%20about%20politics.%20It%20is%20a%20fight%20for%20resources%20and%20benefits.%20From%20disputes%20over%20liquor%20trade%20to%20sand%20mining...%20these%20conflicts%20are%20about%20personal%20gains.%20When%20a%20party%20stays%20in%20power%20for%20too%20long%2C%20such%20issues%20often%20come%20to%20the%20surface.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726755060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Favi68jl8_bjp-congress-flags_625x300_19_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-madhya-pradesh-bjp-leaders-squabble-congress-claims-internal-strife-6603268%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20has%20claimed%20discord%20within%20the%20BJP's%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20ranks%20-%20less%20than%20a%20year%20after%20that%20party%20romped%20to%20victory%20in%20an%20Assembly%20election%2C%20and%20pointed%20to%20statements%20from%20the%20ruling%20party's%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20attacking%20the%20other.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-madhya-pradesh-bjp-leaders-squa