A%20Bansuri%20Swaraj's%20Dig%20Over%20US%20Remarks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20jibe%20at%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20over%20his%20remarks%20during%20his%20recent%20visit%20to%20the%20US%2C%20first-time%20BJP%20MP%20Bansuri%20Swaraj%20has%20said%20she%20would%20switch%20roles%20with%20him%20so%20that%20she%20wouldn't%20embarrass%20India%20on%20an%20international%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20wide-ranging%20discussion%20during%20the%20NDTV%20Yuva%20Conclave%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Ms%20Swaraj%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20trainee%20doctor%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20Atishi%20taking%20over%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Delhi%2C%20and%20said%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20feminist%20dispensations%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20which%20current%20political%20leader%20she%20would%20switch%20roles%20with%2C%20the%20BJP%20MP%20immediately%20said%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%2C%20she%20said%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi...%20So%20that%20when%20I%20go%20abroad%2C%20I%20don't%20embarrass%20my%20country%20on%20an%20international%20platform.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Swaraj's%20remarks%20were%20seen%20as%20a%20dig%20at%20some%20of%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20comments%20during%20the%20US%20visit%2C%20which%20had%20also%20been%20criticised%20by%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnswering%20a%20question%20on%20reservation%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20think%20of%20scrapping%20reservations%20when%20India%20is%20a%20fair%20place%20and%20India%20is%20not%20a%20fair%20place.%26quot%3B%20He%20had%20later%20clarified%20this%20remark%20and%20said%20it%20was%20misrepresented%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Congress%20wanted%20to%20take%20reservation%20beyond%20the%20cap%20of%2050%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20had%20also%20spoken%20about%20religious%20freedom%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsking%20a%20Sikh%20member%20of%20the%20audience%20his%20name%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20had%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20fight%20is%20about%20whether%20he%2C%20as%20a%20Sikh%2C%20is%20going%20to%20be%20allowed%20to%20wear%20a%20turban%20in%20India%3B%20or%20whether%2C%20he%2C%20as%20a%20Sikh%2C%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20wear%20a%20kada%20in%20India%3B%20or%20whether%20he%2C%20as%20a%20Sikh%2C%20is%20allowed%20to%20go%20to%20a%20gurdwara.%20That's%20what%20the%20fight%20is%20about%2C%20and%20not%20just%20for%20him%2C%20but%20for%20all%20religions%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%20Rape%20And%20Murder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Swaraj%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20lawyer%20and%20was%20designated%20a%20senior%20advocate%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20recently%2C%20said%20she%20had%20represented%20the%20petitioner%20on%20whose%20petition%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20trainee%20doctor%20at%20the%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20last%20month%20was%20transferred%20from%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20to%20the%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20politicising%2C%20one%20key%20issue%20is%20that%20a%20serious%20crime%20like%20rape%20and%20murder%20was%20sought%20to%20be%20covered%20up%20as%20a%20suicide.%20In%20the%20last%20hearing%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20you%20cannot%20pass%20legislation%20which%20restricts%20the%20working%20hours%20of%20women.%20You%20cannot%20say%20we%20cannot%20ensure%20your%20safety%20so%20women%20doctors%20can%20work%20only%20for%2012%20hours.%20Your%20incompetence%20or%20incompetence%20of%20a%20state%20machinery%20cannot%20be%20the%20reason%20to%20restrict%20the%20freedom%20of%20women%20or%20clip%20a%20woman's%20wings%2C%20that%20time%20has%20passed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20MP%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20saying%20this%20as%20a%20citizen%20of%20this%20country%2C%20not%20as%20a%20politician.%20It%20is%20time%20for%20all%20of%20us%20to%20come%20together%2C%20raise%20our%20voice%20and%20say%20that%20the%20responsibility%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20women%20is%20not%20on%20women%20alone%2C%20but%20on%20men%20as%20well.%20We%20need%20to%20educate%20our%20boys%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20the%20legislation%20-%20the%20Aparajita%20Woman%20and%20Child%20(West%20Bengal%20Criminal%20Laws%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202024%20-%20introduced%20by%20the%20Bengal%20government%20after%20the%20gruesome%20crime%2C%20Ms%20Swaraj%20termed%20it%20an%20%26quot%3Beyewash%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(Bengal%20chief%20minister)%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20government%20is%20cornered%20and%20has%20question%20marks%20over%20it%20and%20this%20legislation%20was%20passed%20to%20assuage%20the%20public.%20There%20was%20not%20even%20a%20proper%20debate.%20Legislation%20needs%20to%20be%20debated%2C%20that's%20the%20whole%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20MP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20that%20while%20laws%20exist%2C%20the%20focus%20has%20to%20be%20on%20awareness%20and%20implementation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20changing%20the%20societal%20mindset.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDelhi%20Elections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20she%20felt%20the%20BJP%20was%20lacking%20in%20its%20Delhi%20strategy%20in%20some%20way%20and%20found%20itself%20reacting%20to%20the%20AAP's%20moves%20-%20like%20the%20shock%20resignation%20as%20chief%20minister%20by%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20is%20being%20replaced%20by%20Delhi%20minister%20Atishi%20-%20Ms%20Swaraj%20said%20that%20was%20not%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelhi%20is%20getting%20a%20woman%20chief%20minister%20for%20the%20third%20time.%20I%20congratulate%20Atishi%2C%20but%20I%20was%20disappointed%20when%20she%20said%20Delhi%20has%20only%20one%20chief%20minister%20-%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%20She%20turned%20the%20clock%20back%20on%20women's%20empowerment%20100%20years%20with%20that%20statement.%20Will%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20continue%20to%20enjoy%20the%20fruits%20of%20power%20without%20any%20responsibility%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20MP%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Feminist%20Government'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnswering%20a%20question%20from%20a%20young%20woman%20in%20the%20audience%20on%20feminism%20and%20why%20there%20wasn't%20enough%20of%20a%20discussion%20on%20it%2C%20the%20BJP%20MP%20said%20such%20conversations%20are%20easier%20when%20labels%20are%20not%20used%2C%20because%20that%20leads%20to%20people%20having%20a%20more%20open%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Swaraj%20also%20asserted%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20feminist%20ever%20and%20went%20on%20to%20give%20three%20examples%20to%20back%20her%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%2C%20she%20said%2C%20was%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20has%20had%20two%20women%20in%20the%20Cabinet%20Committee%20on%20Security%2C%20which%20has%20the%20PM%20and%20the%20ministers%20for%20defence%2C%20home%20affairs%2C%20finance%20and%20external%20affairs%20as%20members.%20The%20first%20was%20Ms%20Swaraj's%20mother%2C%20Sushma%20Swaraj%2C%20and%20then%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20examples%20given%20by%20Bansuri%20Swaraj%20were%20that%20PM%20Modi%20has%20had%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20women%20ministers%20in%20his%20cabinet%20and%20it%20was%20under%20his%20government's%20second%20term%20that%20the%20legislation%20reserving%2033%20per%20cent%20of%20seats%20for%20women%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20Assemblies%20was%20passed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20another%20audience%20member%20asked%20for%20advice%20on%20advancing%20in%20her%20career%20as%20a%20young%20woman%2C%20Ms%20Swaraj%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20privilege%20to%20be%20a%20woman%2C%20embrace%20it.%20The%20more%20arduous%20the%20journey%2C%20the%20greater%20the%20rewards%2C%20don't%20shy%20away%20from%20the%20hard%20work.%20If%20God%20has%20given%20the%20power%20of%20creation%20to%20anyone%2C%20it%20is%20to%20himself%20and%20to%20women.%20You%20are%20a%20force%20to%20be%20reckoned%20with%2C%20keep%20moving%20forward.%20Don't%20pay%20attention%20to%20any%20trolls%20or%20detractors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726753260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fgifm271_bansuri-swaraj-yuva-conclave_625x300_19_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modis-government-one-of-the-most-feminist-ever-bansuri-swaraj-at-ndtv-yuva-conclave-6602582%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22aking%20a%20jibe%20at%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20over%20his%20remarks%20during%20his%20recent%20visit%20to%20the%20US%2C%20first-time%20BJP%20MP%20Bansuri%20Swaraj%20has%20said%20she%20would%20switch%20roles%20with%20him%20so%20that%20she%20wouldn't%20embarrass%20India%20on%20an%20international%20platform.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modis-government-one-of-the-most-feminist-ever-bansuri-swaraj-at-ndtv-yuva-conclave-6602582%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Guinea%20stadium%20massacre%20fugitive%20extradited%20from%20Liberia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726753126000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F203e%2Flive%2Fbddda5b0-7647-11ef-b312-35e76b118384.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc4g4p93l530o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Claude%20Pivi%2C%20Guinea's%20most%20wanted%20fugitive%2C%20has%20been%20on%20the%20run%20since%20last%20year's%20dramatic%20prison%20break.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A52%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc4g4p93l5