%20the%20Opposition%20block.%20The%20party%20is%20questioning%20the%20%26quot%3Bfine%20print%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20proposal%20of%20the%20Kovind%20Committee%20that%20has%20been%20adopted%20by%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20and%20suggesting%20that%20the%20matter%20not%20be%20rushed%20like%20the%20farm%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJD%2C%20once%20known%20for%20providing%20issue-based%20support%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20was%20routed%20by%20the%20national%20party%20in%20the%20assembly%20election%20held%20earlier%20this%20year.%20%C2%A0Shortly%20after%20that%2C%20Naveen%20Patnaik%2C%20who%20was%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Odisha%20for%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20BJD%20now%20means%20business%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Bno%20more%20support%20to%20BJP%2C%20only%20opposition%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20BJD%20MP%20Sasmit%20Patra%2C%20who%20is%20also%20spokesman%20admitted%20a%20change%20in%20their%20stand.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20had%20initially%20supported%20the%20idea%20of%20'One%20Nation%20One%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I'm%20a%20little%20concerned%20about%20how%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20is%20looking%20at%20this%20entire%20'One%20Nation%20One%20election'.%20What%20is%20the%20fine%20print%3F%20It%20has%20not%20been%20made%20public%20so%20far%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20he%20added%2C%20opens%20up%20a%20huge%20grey%20area%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BOne%20nation%20one%20election%26quot%3B%20plan%2C%20which%20envisages%C2%A0%20simultaneous%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20and%20local%20bodies%20polls%20shortly%20after%C2%A0%20.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20knows%20what%20happens%20if%20there%20is%20a%20hung%20assembly%20or%20there%20is%20an%20early%20dissolution%20of%20the%20assembly%20or%20the%20parliament...%20What%20happens%20if%20tomorrow%20there%20is%20a%20constitutional%20crisis...%20%C2%A0What%20happens%20if%20there%20is%20a%20demand%20for%20an%20early%20dissolution%20that%20comes%20in%20through%20a%20vote%20of%20no%20confidence%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20unanswered%20questions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20I%20hear%20from%20the%20media%20reports%20that%20they're%20going%20to%20probably%20table%20it%20in%20the%20Parliament.%20I%20would%20suggest%20let%20it%20go%20through%20legislative%20scrutiny.%20Don't%20rush%20it%20like%20you%20rush%20the%20farm%20laws.%20Once%20you%20rush%20something%20like%20the%20farm%20laws%2C%20it%20will%20be%20replete%20with%20many%20problems%20later%20on%2C'%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20final%20suggestion%20-%20%26quot%3BLet's%20have%20a%20wider%20consultation%20not%20only%20with%20the%20political%20parties%20but%20across%20all%20the%20stakeholders%20of%20civil%20society%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20contended%20that%20the%20%26quot%3BOne%20nation%20one%20election%26quot%3B%20plan%20is%20not%20only%20anti-democratic%20and%20unconstitutional%2C%20it%20is%20also%20impractical.%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20has%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Ban%20attempt%20to%20divert%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20public%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImplementing%20the%20%26quot%3BOne%20nation%20one%20election%26quot%3B%20plan%20would%20involve%20at%20least%20six%20bills%20to%20amend%20the%20Constitution%20and%20the%20government%20would%20require%20two-third%20majority%20in%20parliament.%20While%20the%20NDA%20has%20a%20simple%20majority%20in%20both%20houses%20of%20parliament%2C%20getting%20two-thirds%20majority%20in%20either%20house%20could%20prove%20a%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ef%20the%20245%20seats%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20NDA%20has%20112%2C%20the%20Opposition%20parties%2085.%20For%20a%20two-thirds%20majority%2C%20the%20government%20needs%20at%20least%20164%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20NDA%20has%20292%20of%20545%20seats.%20The%20two-thirds%20majority%20mark%20stands%20at%20364.%20%C2%A0But%20the%20situation%20could%20be%20dynamic%2C%20since%20the%20majority%20would%20be%20counted%20only%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20members%20present%20and%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJD%2C%20once%20the%20BJP's%20friend%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20which%20helped%20several%20contentious%20bills%20pass%2C%20has%20opposed%20the%20BJP%20in%20multiple%20issues%20since%20its%20assembly%20polls%20defeat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20reply%20to%20the%20Motion%20of%20Thanks%20to%20the%20President's%20address%20during%20the%20inaugural%20session%20of%20parliament%20after%20the%20election%2C%20the%20party's%20nine%20MPs%20joined%20the%20Opposition's%20walkout%20over%20his%20remarks%20on%20Congress's%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20now%20has%20nine%20MPs%20in%20%C2%A0the%20%C2%A0Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20none%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20simultaneous%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20election%20in%20May-June%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%2020%20of%2021%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%2078%20of%20147%20assembly%20seats%20of%20Odisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726752600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fbmtfkefg_bjd-sasmit-patra_625x300_19_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-one-nation-one-election-naveen-patnaiks-party-bjd-tweaks-stand-asks-for-fine-print-cites-farm-laws-6602903%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Naveen%20Patnaik's%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%2C%20once%20a%20supporter%20of%20'One%20Nation%20One%20Election%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20tweaked%20its%20stand%20on%20the%20issue.%20Though%20not%20so%20strident%2C%20its%20current%20concerns%20on%20the%20matter%20echoes%20that%20of%20the%20Opposition%20block.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C