2C%20the%20watchdog%20has%20also%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20country%20needs%20to%20improve%20its%20system%20as%20the%20economy%20continues%20to%20grow%2C%20pointing%20to%20a%20need%20for%20faster%20trials%20for%20money%20laundering%20and%20terrorist%20financing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20placed%20in%20the%20regular%20follow-up%20category%2C%20a%20distinction%20it%20shares%20with%20only%20four%20other%20G20%20countries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mutual%20evaluation%20report%20says%20a%20joint%20FATF-APG%20(Asia%2FPacific%20Group%20on%20Money%20Laundering)-EAG%20(Eurasian%20group%20on%20combating%20money%20laundering%20and%20financing%20of%20terrorism)%20%C2%A0assessment%20of%20India's%20measures%20to%20tackle%20illicit%20finance%20has%20concluded%20that%20India%20has%20implemented%20an%20anti-money%20laundering%20and%20counter-terrorist%20financing%20(AML%2FCFT)%20framework%20which%20is%20achieving%20good%20results.%20The%20areas%20in%20which%20these%20results%20have%20been%20seen%20include%20risk%20understanding%2C%20access%20to%20beneficial%20ownership%20information%20and%20depriving%20criminals%20of%20their%20assets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20says%20authorities%20in%20India%20make%20good%20use%20of%20financial%20intelligence%20and%20cooperate%20effectively%2C%20both%20domestically%20and%20internationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20evaluation%20noted%20that%20India%20is%20the%20largest%20country%20in%20the%20world%20by%20population%20and%20has%20the%20largest%20diaspora.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20lower-middle-income%20country%20with%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20fastest-growing%20economies%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20the%20fifth-largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world.%20%C2%A0India's%20main%20money%20laundering%20risks%2C%20the%20report%20says%2C%20originate%20from%20illegal%20activities%20within%20the%20country%20-%20relating%20primarily%20to%20fraud%2C%20including%20cyber-enabled%20fraud%2C%20corruption%20and%20drug%20trafficking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20pursues%20money%20laundering%20cases%20related%20to%20fraud%20and%20forgery%20in%20line%20with%20predicate%20crime%20(a%20criminal%20act%20that%20is%20a%20component%20of%20a%20larger%20crime)%20risks%20to%20a%20large%20extent%2C%20the%20report%20says%2C%20but%20needs%20to%20do%20more%20for%20some%20other%20offences%20such%20as%20human%20trafficking%20and%20drug%20trafficking.%20The%20country%2C%20it%20said%2C%20needs%20to%20address%20the%20backlog%20of%20money%20laundering%20cases%20pending%20conclusion%20of%20court%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETerror%20Threats%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20says%20India%20faces%20serious%20terrorism%20and%20terrorist%20financing%20threats%2C%20including%20related%20to%20ISIL%20(Islamic%20State%20of%20Iraq%20and%20the%20Levant)%20or%20al-Qaeda%20active%20in%20and%20around%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20Praising%20India's%20emphasis%20on%20disruption%20and%20prevention%20and%20its%20ability%20to%20conduct%20complex%20financial%20investigations%2C%20the%20evaluation%20points%20to%20a%20need%20for%20focusing%20on%20concluding%20prosecutions%20and%20convicting%20and%20sanctioning%20terrorist%20financiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20area%20pointed%20out%20by%20the%20report%20is%20a%20need%20to%20ensure%20that%20measures%20aimed%20at%20preventing%20the%20non-profit%20sector%20from%20being%20abused%20for%20terrorist%20financing%20are%20implemented%20in%20line%20with%20a%20risk-based%20approach%2C%20including%20by%20conducting%20outreach%20to%20such%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinancial%20Inclusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppreciating%20India's%20steps%20towards%20financial%20inclusion%2C%20the%20report%20said%20the%20proportion%20of%20the%20population%20with%20bank%20accounts%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%2C%20due%20diligence%20for%20small%20accounts%20is%20taking%20place%20and%20reliance%20on%20digital%20payment%20systems%20has%20been%20encouraged.%20These%20efforts%20have%20supported%20financial%20transparency%2C%20contributing%20to%20efforts%20to%20tackle%20anti-money%20laundering%20and%20counter-terrorist%20financing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20the%20size%20and%20institutional%20complexity%20of%20the%20Indian%20system%2C%20Indian%20authorities%20cooperate%20and%20coordinate%20effectively%20on%20matters%20dealing%20with%20illicit%20financial%20flows%2C%20including%20the%20use%20of%20financial%20intelligence.%20India%20also%20achieved%20positive%20results%20in%20international%20cooperation%2C%20asset%20recovery%20and%20implementing%20targeted%20financial%20sanctions%20for%20proliferation%20financing%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20authorities%20also%20have%20a%20comprehensive%20understanding%20of%20the%20money%20laundering%2C%20terrorism%20and%20proliferation%20financing%20risks%2C%20it%20says%2C%20but%20also%20points%20to%20a%20need%20for%20sharing%20insights%20on%20them%20with%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20says%20there%20is%20a%20good%20understanding%20of%20risk%20and%20application%20of%20preventative%20measures%20in%20the%20financial%20sector%2C%20especially%20by%20commercial%20banks%2C%20but%20less%20so%20by%20some%20other%20smaller%20financial%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFollowing%20the%20assessment%2C%20India%20is%20placed%20in%20'regular%20follow-up'%20and%2C%20in%20line%20with%20procedures%2C%20will%20report%20back%20to%20the%20Plenary%20in%20three%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726744260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-04%2F0a19pbic_terrorist-generic-ndtv-file_625x300_16_April_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffatf-mutual-evaluation-report-india-anti-terror-watchdog-praises-indias-measures-flags-slow-money-laundering-trials-6601689%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Terror%2