C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Battery%20Smart%3A%20Startup%20Does%201%20Lakh%20Electric%20Vehicle%20Battery%20Swaps%20Daily%3B%20Earns%2063%20Cr%20in%20Revenue%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBattery%20Smart%20%E2%80%94%20a%20market%20leader%20in%20facilitating%20battery%20swapping%20for%20two%20and%20three-wheeler%20electric%20vehicles%20(EVs)%20in%20India%20%E2%80%94%20reached%20a%20significant%20landmark%20last%20month.%20On%207%20August%2C%20the%20Delhi-based%20venture%20founded%20by%20IIT%20Kanpur%20graduates%20Pulkit%20Khurana%20and%20Siddharth%20Sikka%20announced%20that%20it%20had%20surpassed%20one%20lakh%20daily%20swaps%20on%20its%20network%20of%20over%2055%2C000%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20launch%20of%20its%20first%20swap%20station%20in%20Janakpuri%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20in%20June%202020%2C%20Battery%20Smart%20has%20rapidly%20expanded%20its%20network.%20With%201%2C200%20stations%20now%20spread%20across%20more%20than%2035%20cities%20in%20India%2C%20the%20Delhi-based%20electric%20mobility%20venture%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20leading%20player%20in%20the%20battery%20swapping%20sector%2C%20surpassing%2045%20million%20cumulative%20swaps%20to%20date%2C%20they%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202019%2C%20the%20objective%20of%20establishing%20Battery%20Smart%20was%20to%20make%20%E2%80%9CEV%20adoption%20simple%2C%20economical%20and%20accessible%20through%20a%20unique%20partner-led%20model%E2%80%9D%2C%20says%20Siddharth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20battery%20swapping%20technology%20does%20for%20the%20electric%20mobility%20sector%20in%20India%20is%20address%20anxieties%20over%20the%20cost%20of%20EVs%20(since%20batteries%20make%20up%20as%20much%20as%2040%25%20of%20the%20production%20cost%20of%20a%20typical%20EV)%2C%20lack%20of%20adequate%20charging%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20the%20time%20taken%20to%20charge%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20context%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%