20of%20the%20Year%20award!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGrowing%20up%20amidst%20wildlife%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFaridabad%20residents%20Shivang%20and%20Kahini%20quickly%20noticed%20their%20daughter%20Shreyovi%E2%80%99s%20innate%20love%20for%20nature%20and%20wildlife%2C%20and%20they%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20take%20her%20outdoors%20whenever%20possible.%20With%20Shivang%20spending%20over%20300%20days%20a%20year%20in%20the%20field%2C%20it%20meant%20long%20stretches%20away%20from%20the%20family.%20Taking%20Shreyovi%20along%20on%20his%20wildlife%20expeditions%20became%20not%20only%20a%20way%20for%20her%20to%20connect%20with%20nature%20but%20also%20a%20special%20opportunity%20for%20father-daughter%20bonding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshreyovi-1726580937.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shreyovi%20with%20her%20parents%20on%20a%20safari.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshreyovi-1726580937.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshreyovi-1726580937-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshreyovi-1726580937-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshreyovi-1726580937-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshreyovi-1726580937-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366262%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShreyovi%20with%20her%20parents%20on%20a%20safari.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20noticed%20Shreyovi%E2%80%99s%20gradual%20inclination%20towards%20photography.%20She%20always%20loved%20being%20in%20the%20field%20with%20me.%20She%20saw%20equipment%20all%20around%20her%20and%20wanted%20to%20try%20her%20hand%20at%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shivang%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Shreyovi%20was%20about%20four%2C%20her%20parents%20gave%20her%20Kahini%E2%80%99s%20old%20point-and-shoot%20camera%2C%20sparking%20her%20journey%20into%20photography.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20camera%20had%20a%20good%20zoom%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shivang%20recalls%2C%20and%20Shreyovi%20loved%20experimenting%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurrounded%20by%20photographers%20and%20naturalists%2C%20she%20had%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363139%2Fjai-dhar-gupta-vijay-dhasmana-biosphere-rajaji-national-park-uttarakhand-rewilding-forest-wildlife%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperfect%20environment%20to%20hone%20her%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20receiving%20guidance%20from%20some%20of%20the%20best%20in%20the%20field.%20By%20the%20age%20of%20six%2C%20she%20had%20already%20picked%20up%20her%20first%20professional%20camera%2C%20marking%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20her%20budding%20photography%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20bit%20heavy%2C%20but%20I%20was%20so%20excited%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shreyovi.%20With%20mentorship%20from%20the%20photographers%20at%20Nature%20Wanderers%2C%20Shreyovi%20began%20learning%20the%20finer%20aspects%20of%20photography%20%E2%80%94%20framing%2C%20angles%2C%20camera%20settings%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20age%20of%2010%2C%20she%20had%20already%20visited%2010%20national%20parks%20and%20Masai%20Mara%2C%20spending%2030%20to%2040%20days%20a%20year%20in%20the%20wild%20on%20safaris%20and%20expeditions.%20For%20a%20young%20child%2C%20navigating%20the%20outdoors%20isn%E2%80%99t%20always%20easy%2C%20especially%20with%20the%20amount%20of%20walking%20required%2C%20but%20Shreyovi%20embraced%20the%20challenge