llege%20as%20founder%20dean%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Soumya%20conceded%20to%20go.%20When%20asked%20how%20she%20managed%20the%20project%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20she%20simply%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20collaboration%20and%20cooperation%20by%20the%20State%20Government%20helped%20expedite%20things.%20I%20have%20realised%20that%20barriers%20can%20always%20be%20overcome.%20All%20you%20need%20to%20do%20is%20take%20challenges%20and%20turn%20them%20into%20opportunities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReeling%20from%20this%20success%2C%20Dr%20Soumya%20returned%20to%20her%20role%20as%20dean%20in%20Kolkata.%20But%20then%20she%20got%20a%20call.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20%5BBhupender%20Yadav%5D%20was%20keen%20that%20I%20go%20to%20Nagaland%20and%20help%20set%20up%20the%20medical%20college%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Family%20is%20important%3B%20career%20is%20too%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fem%3Espoke%20to%20six%20individuals%20from%20Nagaland%20to%20get%20their%20insights%20on%20one%20question%3A%20Do%20you%20feel%20alienated%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20stood%20out%20for%20me%20was%20how%20many%20of%20the%20responders%20said%20that%20their%20fear%20of%20discrimination%20had%20forced%20them%20to%20live%20a%20life%20of%20confinement.%20They%20never%20ventured%20outside%20their%20home%20territory.%20The%20article%20sheds%20light%20on%20how%20perceptions%20about%20the%20Naga%20community%20are%20often%20rooted%20in%20stereotypes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20Dr%20Soumya%2C%20who%20was%20debating%20a%20move%20to%20the%20Northeast%20in%202022%2C%20was%20confronted%20with%20this%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fvinyasa-earth-1725974702.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20team%20of%20staff%20and%20heads%20at%20the%20Nagaland%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20and%20Research%20(NIMSR)%20in%20Kohima%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fvinyasa-earth-1725974702.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fvinyasa-earth-1725974702-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fvinyasa-earth-1725974702-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fvinyasa-earth-1725974702-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fvinyasa-earth-1725974702-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365386%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%20of%20staff%20and%20heads%20at%20the%20Nagaland%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20and%20Research%20(NIMSR)%20in%20Kohima.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20have%20various%20stigmas%20around%20Nagaland.%20This%20was%20creating%20a%20challenging%20situation%20for%20me%20amongst%20my%20friends%20and%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20sighs.%20Though%20the%20reasons%20to%20stay%20back%20in%20Kolkata%20were%20stronger%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lucrative%20and%20steady%20job%2C%20a%20great%20family%2C%20and%20a%20home%20%E2%80%94%20she%20says%2C%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinner%20calling%E2%80%9D%20compelled%20her%20to%20choose%20Option%20B.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20heard%20of%20how%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F239559%2Fips-hero-free-upsc-coaching-nagaland-pritpal-kaur-batra-tuensang-noklak-district-drugs-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20of%20Nagaland%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20to%20travel%20to%20other%20states%20for%20medical%20education%2C%E2%