dards%20for%20vehicles%20and%20their%20components.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20an%20important%20development%20in%20advancing%20an%20indigenous%20EV%20infrastructure%20in%20India%20given%20how%20it%20has%20been%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F280479%2Findia-electric-vehicle-revolution-ev-charging-infrastructure-network-experts-future%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0unable%20to%20keep%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0with%20the%20growing%20fleet%20of%20domestic%20EVs.%20What%E2%80%99s%20more%2C%20the%20indigenous%20manufacturing%20of%20its%20(charging%20infrastructure)%20key%20components%20is%20at%20a%20nascent%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20does%20the%20ARAI%20certification%20mean%20for%20Plugzmart%E2%80%99s%2060kW%20DC%20fast%20charger%3F%20This%20certification%20for%20the%20Chennai-based%20startup%E2%80%99s%20fast%20charger%20and%20proprietary%20controller%20card%20signifies%20their%20compliance%20with%20stringent%20operational%20safety%20standards%20and%20efficiency%20norms%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307090%2Fchennai-startup-builds-homegrown-iot-enabled-smart-ev-chargers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0back%20in%20December%202022%2C%20co-founder%20Ragavendra%20Ravichandran%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20majority%20of%20EV%20chargers%20in%20India%20today%20are%20being%20imported%20and%20are%20of%20low%20quality.%20They%E2%80%99re%20largely%20imported%20from%20China.%20%5BThis%20is%20because%5D%20Chinese%20chargers%20are%20priced%20low%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20support%20from%20Chinese%20manufacturers%20once%20installed%2C%20which%20is%20a%20key%20issue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%2012