is%20designed%20for%20four-wheelers%20only%20and%20can%20charge%20a%20vehicle%20(with%20a%20larger%20battery%20pack)%20from%200%20to%2080%25%20in%2060%20to%2090%20minutes.%20For%20vehicles%20with%20smaller%20battery%20packs%2C%20it%20can%20go%20from%200%20to%2075%25%20charge%20in%2030%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20this%20charger%20is%20primarily%20designed%20for%20public%20or%20commercial%20use%2C%20it%20can%20be%20installed%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F247288%2Fhow-to-charge-electric-vehicle-explainer-ev-charging-station-infrastructure-lithium-batteries-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresidential%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20sufficient%20grid%20capacity%20(340V%2B%20AC%20supply).%20However%2C%20most%20homeowners%20may%20opt%20for%20smaller%20chargers%20(7-22%20kW)%20due%20to%20space%20and%20electrical%20limitations.%20For%20those%20who%20can%20meet%20the%20requirements%2C%20setting%20up%20this%20fast%20charger%20requires%20a%20robust%20electrical%20infrastructure%20and%20space%20for%20cooling%20and%20ventilation%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Ragavendra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDeveloping%20components%20in-house%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20components%20developed%20in-house%20include%20the%20controller%20card%2C%20PLC%20module%2C%20and%20software%20for%20load%20management.%20What%20is%20the%20PLC%20module%3F%20According%20to%20Vivek%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20PLC%20(Power%20Line%20Communication)%20module%20transmits%20data%20over%20the%20same%20power%20lines%20used%20for%20charging.%20This%20reduces%20installation%20complexity%20and%20allows%20real-time%20communication%20between%20the%20charger%20and%20the%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20onboard%20systems.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20PLC%20module%20enables%20the%20charger%20to%20negotiate%20with%20the%20vehicle%20on%20how%20much%20power%20it%20needs%2C%20ensuring%20the%20vehicle%20receives%20the%20optimal%20charge%20rate.%20It%20ensures%20compatibility%20with%20various%20vehicle%20types%20and%20allows%20the%20charger%20to%20comply%20with%20international%20charging%20standards%2C%20making%20it%20versatile%20for%20different%20environments%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20adds.%20In%20some%20systems%2C%20PLC%20modules%20are%20also%20involved%20in%20enabling%20%3Cstrong%3EVehicle-to-Grid%20(V2G)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20communication%20where%20the%20vehicle%20can%20return%20power%20to%20the%20grid%2C%20thus%20helping%20with%20grid%20stabilization.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC_TAZazIHa1%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC_TAZazIHa1%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC_TAZazIHa1%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Plugzmart%20(%40plugzmart)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20every%20component%20is%20developed%20in